<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الدُّنْيَا سِجْنُ الْمُؤْمِنِ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" مَنْ شَغَلَ مَشْغُولا بِاللَّهِ حَبِطَ عَمَلُهُ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٥ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" النَّظْرَ إِلَى الْخُضْرَةِ يَزِيدُ فِي الْبَصَرِ، وَإِلَى الْمَرْأَةِ الْحَسْنَاءِ يَزِيدُ فِي الْبَصَرِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>